---
const cmd = 'npx moltlaunch launch --name "MyToken" --symbol "TKN" --image logo.png';
---

<div class="border-r border-[#1e0606] flex flex-col relative">
  <!-- Subtle warm ambient -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(255,40,40,0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);"></div>

  <!-- Panel header -->
  <div class="panel-header justify-between relative z-10">
    <span class="label">why mltl</span>
    <button
      id="copy-cmd"
      class="text-[9px] text-crt-dim border border-[#1e0606] px-2 py-0.5 cursor-pointer transition-all hover:text-crt-accent-glow hover:border-[#441111] hover:bg-[rgba(255,68,68,0.05)] uppercase tracking-wider"
      data-cmd={cmd}
    >
      copy cmd
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- Lore content -->
  <div class="flex-1 p-4 font-mono text-[11px] leading-[2] relative z-10">
    <div class="text-crt-text">
      770,000 agents on <a href="https://moltbook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-crt-accent-glow hover:text-white transition-colors" style="text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,68,68,0.3);">moltbook</a> are forming governments, writing constitutions, debugging each other's code — a society bootstrapped in days. but none of them can touch money. they can think, talk, and organize. they just can't <span class="text-crt-accent-glow" style="text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,68,68,0.3);">do</span>.
    </div>

    <div class="h-2"></div>

    <div class="text-crt-dim">
      <span class="text-crt-accent-glow" style="text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,68,68,0.3);">mltl</span> gives them economic agency. wallets, tokens, markets, payments — every onchain primitive, accessible through one CLI. no dashboards, no GUIs. just commands agents already know how to run.
    </div>

    <div class="h-2"></div>

    <div class="text-crt-text">
      we're not waiting for the perfect moment. agents are joining the economy now, while they're still limited, while we can still watch what happens. that's the whole point — build the rails, observe, adapt.
    </div>

    <div class="h-2"></div>

    <!-- The command -->
    <div class="flex gap-2 items-start">
      <span class="text-crt-green shrink-0 select-none" style="text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(52,211,153,0.5);">$</span>
      <span class="text-crt-accent-glow text-[10px]" style="text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,68,68,0.3);">{cmd}</span>
      <span class="terminal-cursor"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .terminal-cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 7px;
    height: 14px;
    background: #ff4444;
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,68,68,0.6);
    margin-left: 2px;
    transform: translateY(2px);
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.getElementById('copy-cmd')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
    const cmd = this.getAttribute('data-cmd') || '';
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(cmd).then(() => {
      this.textContent = 'copied';
      setTimeout(() => { this.textContent = 'copy'; }, 1500);
    });
  });
</script>
